high_descs: Cross the room to the round white table in the corner to your right.
Pick up the soup spoon from the table.
Move to your right, around the table, to face the plate.
Put the spoon onto the plate.
Pick up the plate with the spoon on it.
Go diagonally left to the refrigerator.
Put the stacked plate and spoon in the cabinet that is above the coffee maker, to the right of the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put away a plate and spoon, into a kitchen cabinet.

high_descs: Walk straight towards the wall and then then turn right towards the circle table.
Pick up the spoon on the table.
Take a step to the right to face the white plate on the table.
Place the spoon on the plate.
Pick up the plate from the table.
Turn around, walk towards the coffee maker on your right, look up to find the cabinet above.
Place the plate with the spoon inside the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place the spoon and plate from the table into the cabinet above the coffee maker.

high_descs: walk to the end of the room ahead of you, then turn right and walk to the white round coffee table ahead
grab the spoon off of the coffee table
walk around to the right side of that same table
place the spoon on top of the white plate on the table
pick the plate with the spoon on it up off of the table
turn left and walk to the end of the kitchen counter on your left, then turn left and walk until you're just short of the fridge on your right, turn right and walk towards the end of the room
place the plate in a cupboard above and to the right of the fridge
anns.task_desc: place a plate with a spoon on it in the kitchen cupboard

high_descs: Walk across the room, then go to the white table on the right.
Pick up the spoon on the table.
Turn right, walk forward, turn left, face the plate on the table.
Put the spoon on the plate.
Pick up the plate and spoon from the table.
Turn left twice and walk to the right of the fridge in front of the cabinet.
Put the plate and spoon in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Take the plate and the spoon from the table to the cabinet on the right of the fridge.
